{"tid":2310651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅孖男友DAWN拍內衣廣告　濕身拍攝相當誘人","createTime":"2020-12-03T11:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T13:37:26.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"830aec8c8086b65c2169f0fd3a476ca91268650b","tid":2310651,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"韓國「性感小馬」泫雅昨日（2日）在IG上傳，與男子DAWN拍攝內衣廣告的花絮影片，二人互向對方拋花瓣，大派閃光彈外，兩人的好身材吸睛到不得了。另一輯照片中，泫雅甚至濕身拍攝，火辣程度爆表！<br />\n<br />\n泫雅擔任內衣品牌代言人已一段時間，每輯都照片都非常驚艷，就連女生都羨慕她的好身材。近日泫雅與男友DAWN孖住一同拍廣告，兩人在片場不但互拋花瓣，又大方在鏡頭前親咀，隔住熒幕都感受二人Sweet爆！泫雅和化妝師也率先公開一張濕身拍攝的新照，見到身穿白色上衣的泫雅浸在浴缸濕身拍攝，就算不用刻意賣弄性感，已非常誘人，粉絲都表示非常期待更多成品公開。"},{"pid":"b5a5b189c84a8b6fe9a34387ffaf24fbf6bde823","tid":2310651,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201203/411159341471633408623150.jpeg/Ee0MCCRSnGWbn94BLAtzoNtabN18V20ezS39Mc0t_TE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201203%2F411159341471633408623150.jpeg%2FEe0MCCRSnGWbn94BLAtzoNtabN18V20ezS39Mc0t_TE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b1380e99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201203/411159486577774592536248.jpeg/bYNz2EWZG2CaNRqSkxxG4TDnJsI5qU7o7S2nsO0tp7A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201203%2F411159486577774592536248.jpeg%2FbYNz2EWZG2CaNRqSkxxG4TDnJsI5qU7o7S2nsO0tp7A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f2a2765b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201203/411160157834186752315460.jpeg/MaSrFY8sVrMvPNYifkZvW-dghcRpPBhx-1QKVvtUClY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201203%2F411160157834186752315460.jpeg%2FMaSrFY8sVrMvPNYifkZvW-dghcRpPBhx-1QKVvtUClY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=51e2b2bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d45b5f89f61b7f03c10bba9e659